caption:
🔥Commissions are open! 🔥

Prices include simple background. Slots are first come-first serve basis.

I don’t do porn, gore, intense violence, I reserve a right to decline any commission if I’m not comfortable with something.

• If you have any questions you can message me.

• If you are decide to commision me, send details on email faietiya@gmail.com I’ll send you rough sketch for approval. After your approval I’ll send you paypal invoise and start paint after recieving of payment.

Also I made ko-fi page  and you can suport me there or by rebloging this post! Thanks!
